                "3 GeV."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "STTA"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Each stack contained Uranium Target and Aluminum",
                "foils served as recoil catchers and monitors of the",
                "Proton Beam intensity."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Depending upon the Products studied,",
                "irradiations lasted from five minutes to a few hours."
